### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/api/health

###

### Generate Soal Pilihan Ganda
POST http://localhost:5000/api/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic": "Rekursif dalam Python",
  "difficulty": "medium",
  "question_type": "multiple_choice",
  "num_questions": 3
}

###

### Generate Soal Benar/Salah
POST http://localhost:5000/api/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic": "Konsep OOP dalam Java",
  "difficulty": "easy",
  "question_type": "true_false",
  "num_questions": 3
}

###

### Generate Soal Esai
POST http://localhost:5000/api/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic": "Algoritma Dijkstra",
  "difficulty": "hard",
  "question_type": "essay",
  "num_questions": 2
}

###

### Ambil Riwayat
GET http://localhost:5000/api/history?limit=10

###

### Ambil Detail Record (ganti ID sesuai hasil)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/history/1

###

### Lihat Log Permintaan
GET http://localhost:5000/api/logs?limit=20
